  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was of course the personal and-- and emotional side, which basically was framed in and-- and sustained by my three sisters and of course my wife, Tagora, and my two children, Ariela and Nuri, who to me-- beyond the-- in the case of my sister, it's beyond the-- the common history-- and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the very close, personal friendship, I-- I think there are no closer friends in the world that I can think of than my sisters and-- and-- and myself, and they among themselves and with me-- and my family, which to me is an essential and-- and a very central element in this perpetuation of Judaism to me.",
      "word_count": 114
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My children represent not only my children, but they represent the continuity of Judaism and of Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it-- in a very real sense, these two things-- plus whatever modest contribution I have been able to make to this goal of-- of assuring the continuity of the Jewish people-- represent on the one hand, in a very real sense, a-- a demonstration of our victory over Hitler.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In a way, we won.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We lost a tremendous amount.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the world has lost a-- a great deal, irreplaceably.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No one can bring the 6 million alive and their potential descendants and their potential achievements and contributions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But-- but we are here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In a very real sense, [SPEAKING HEBREW], we are alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] My family is an integral part of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so I am content [? but ?] not-- not only that I had survived, but that I had lived productively and have contributed-- as I say, however modestly-- to the continuity of our people.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
